              MOVE 0 TO TOTEM-MSG-SIZE
              INSPECT TOTEM-MSG-2 TALLYING TOTEM-MSG-SIZE FOR TRAILING 
           SPACE
              IF TOTEM-MSG-TEXT-POINTER > 1
